    "body": "I would like to be able to not impose a maximum character width via `textwidth`, but still ensure that the length of every line, ignoring the whitespace at the start of the line due to indentation, is limited to a certain amount. This ensures that things like comments are formatted in a readable way.\r\n\r\nI don't think this can be accomplished easily currently (correct me if I'm wrongi). Perhaps a `formatoptions` option can be added?",
